{"version":3,"kind":"Notebook","sha256":"d5ee3dca9d470ee13a0ec109646b02c354c47c32a6bcd2280b3e092ec541e2b8","slug":"currentness","location":"/content/currentness.ipynb","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"Currentness","content_includes_title":false,"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3 (ipykernel)","language":"python"},"numbering":{"title":{"offset":1}},"thumbnail":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/currentness_01-79c2fb8c38fb83829f86d719a9008a33.png","exports":[{"format":"ipynb","filename":"currentness.ipynb","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/currentness-80f777899bb2fac953b972be18fa6749.ipynb"}]},"widgets":{},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-content","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der Currentness Indicator misst, wie aktuell OSM-Elemente sind, indem die Verteilung ihrer neuesten Beiträge analysiert wird.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"key":"dFagSqSx51"}],"key":"fxtWIKFzaS"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Methodik","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"EYB3kDu6Jj"}],"identifier":"methodik","label":"Methodik","html_id":"methodik","implicit":true,"key":"QZ565AtEHf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"-> Intrinsischer Ansatz","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"nmDoHTjb2R"}],"key":"ZE81EshOB0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Der Currentness-Indikator berücksichtigt alle Änderungen an Geometrien und Tags (ohne Löschungen) seit 2008, aggregiert in monatlichen Intervallen. Der Ergebniswert wird als Prozentsatz der Elemente berechnet, die in den letzten 36 Monaten zuletzt bearbeitet wurden, normalisiert auf einen Bereich von 0 bis 1. Jeder Beitrag wird einer von drei Qualitätsstufen zugeordnet:","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1},"end":{"line":6,"column":1}},"key":"kOUGVgTreX"}],"key":"W5W7DbX3pk"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Veraltet (< 0.5): Features, die über einen längeren Zeitraum nicht aktualisiert wurden, werden als veraltet eingestuft. Diese Schwellenwerte werden in Monaten seit dem aktuellen Datum ausgedrückt. Für jede Feature-Klasse wird der relative Anteil der Beiträge berechnet, die in diese Kategorien fallen.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"gNTw8IZdzh"}],"key":"P2tki3QUDY"}],"key":"oPmEDqcOdv"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mittel (0.5 - 0.75): Beiträge, die zuletzt innerhalb eines Zeitraums von 4 bis 8 Jahren bearbeitet wurden, werden als mittel eingestuft.","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"GD0zQXnZ3I"}],"key":"nzhij2383g"}],"key":"fQbd3nKsBT"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Aktuell (> 0.75): Features gelten als aktuell, wenn ihre letzte Bearbeitung in ein vordefiniertes kurzes Zeitfenster fällt.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"x8fkSo5WTJ"}],"key":"QUNHGX8Vgw"}],"key":"HVen4Y5F5w"}],"key":"idsP19L3ri"},{"type":"image","url":"/oqapi-jupyter-book/build/currentness_01